captions.text:
"Quick Change", okay?
Dani, Elidio and Oscar will play.

How does it work?
Every time I say 'change',

they'll have to change the
last thing they have said or done.

I can also say 'more' so they
have to make things bigger,

or say 'less'
to make things smaller.

So, I'll pick up an invisible
object here. What is it?

A 'helmet'. Great. A 'helmet' will be
the motivation of the scene,
"Quick Change" starts now!

Calm down, ma'am, he
wasn't wearing a helmet...

I know that, son, but a thing
like this shoudn't happen...

I know, but you
can't see him now...

- I'm going to sue him.
- So you're not his relative?

- Yes, I am, but...
- Change!

- No, I'm not!
- Change!

- I've never seen this man in my life!
- So, he hit your car?

- No, it was my leg!
- Change!

- No, he hit my pinky finger!
- Change!

My osteoarthritis!
Lord, it hurts!

- Okay, ma'am. I can send you
to an orthopedist... - More!

- I can take you in my arms
to the orthopedist... - More!

- I'll carry you to the master of
orthopedics of Brazil... - All right!

- Now!
- Now!

- Of course I will...
- Thank you!

- The orthopedics master...
- Next!
Is a major son of a bitch!

- But he is a good doctor... - How's my
weight? People say I'm getting fat...

- No way, ma'am... - Watch out, I don't
want my butt crack on camera...
Suzana, call the next one.

- Okay, the patient is coming in.
- Go slower, I'm getting dizzy!
Change the carrying!
Can we do it from here?

- Yes, ma'am, I think you're okay...
- Change!
Change!

Ma'am, I think your osteoarthritis
is okay, you carried me here...
Listen, doc...

I did the carrying test,
she can carry.

- What's wrong with you?
- I think I'm going to die!

- So...
- Change!

- I think I'm going to live!
- Change!
I think I'm horny in my legs...

Are you feeling horny in
the legs for how long now?

It's been a while, my
husband died 50 years ago...

After that, no one ever,
you know......

You have to be careful,
this could go up your...

- Can you give me a kiss?
- Less!

- Can you give me a peck kiss?
- Less!

- Can you cop a feel on me?
- Less!

- Can you blow on me?
- Yes I can, ma'am.

- In the interstice of my fingers?
- Where exactly?
The interstice of my fingers!

Sorry, I didn't understand that.
Where?
The interstice of my fingers!

Ma'am, interstices are the field of
another doctor, I'll carry you to him!

- For God's sake, make it quick!
- Next!
We can do it right here!
All right!

CQC's backstage must be
filled with junk food!

CIA. BARBIXAS DE HUMOR
presented
